<MainLayout metatitle="GALLERY">
  <div class="gallery_heading1"><h1>GALLERY</h1></div>
  <div class="line"></div>

  <div class="gallery_box">
  <div class="gallery_img"><img src="/public/bilder/galleri_billeder/gal5.webp" alt="gallery_img"></div>
  <div class="gallery_text1"><p>Step into Panache, where art takes center stage in an ever-evolving gallery nestled within our vibrant Copenhagen bar. <br><br>
    This isn't just a place to sip cocktails — it’s a hub for creativity and expression and is uniquely tied to the pulse of the city. Our gallery showcases the talent of local artists and our exhibit change regularly. <br><br>

Celebrate the spirit of local creativity and let the art spark conversations, inspire your imagination, or simply provide a moment of quiet reflection amidst the buzz of the bar.

At Panache, art isn't just decoration—it’s a living, breathing part of the experience.</p>
<br><br><br><br>
<div class="artist_h2">
<h2>Are you an artist?</h2> <br><br>
</div>

Send us an email if you're interested in showcasing your art in our bar for our guests to see and buy! We'd love to have a chat and see your amazing art!
<br>
<br>

<a class="buttum" href="mailto:panachecph@gmail.com">
<Buttum text="SEND MAIL"/> 
</a>
</div>
